        "rich-text-about": {
            "type": "rich-text",
            "blocks": {
                "heading": {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "settings": {
                        "heading": "About AD Organics"
                    }
                },
                "text": {
                    "type": "text",
                    "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Our goal is for everyone to live a healthier and happy life, we are more than just food that is why we bringing you the most authentic ingredients some of them rare and some found in our grandmother's kitchen. You feel the magic with AD Organics more than just food it's food that is medicine for souls. And we believe quality should be the first priority. Planet earth is in our hands and we are here to make it greener and healthier. Improving and feeding through our organic produce from our sources. Our goal is to provide fresh and authentic foods with plenty of natural vitamins, nutrition, and antioxidants. No added salt, sugar or colour with our products. We at AD Organics provide you with the same purity as and when they were grown. Our sources and our farmers are our pillars because of their hard work we are here. For them, we try to create a healthy environment where they can sustain better lives for their families. We take pride in the results of the food that we produce and the lives that we help improve in the process.<\/p>"
                    }
                }
            },
            "block_order": [
                "heading",
                "text"
            ]
        },
